Milner on Sadio Man&eacute;: &ldquo;He does his job and does a great job for the team and people see the flair and ability to has and the goals he scores but he does a great job for the team as well and a great member of the dressing room.&quot;<br />
<br />
Milner on Porto: &quot;They&rsquo;re a very good side, it is tough place to come. You heard the crowd there at the end even with the result the way it was so credit to them and they&rsquo;re a good team. We knew it was going to be tough and we wanted to keep a clean sheet.&quot;

Klopp on whether it was the perfect performance: &quot;Klopp: &ldquo;Yes you can say that. It was very professional and very mature in the right moments, very aggressive, good defending, good counter-attacking and keeping the ball.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;In this game it was possible to move them around, usually it&rsquo;s not that easy but it was hard work tonight and in the end the boys enjoyed the work and that&rsquo;s the most important thing.&rdquo;
